Additional Enhancements for Real Elections:
Security:
---Integrate biometric verification or a unique voter identifier (e.g., Aadhaar).
---Use end-to-end encryption to protect voter privacy.
---Store votes on a private blockchain to ensure immutability and transparency.
Scalability:
---Consider using a Layer 2 solution like Polygon for faster transactions and reduced gas fees.
Frontend Integration:
---Build a React or Next.js frontend to provide a user-friendly voting interface.
---Use MetaMask for user authentication and blockchain transactions.
